data.description: **Assumable loan at 3.75% for qualified buyers.**  If you are looking for a truly special property, look no further! This incredible home in the Branch Creek community of Summerville is beautiful inside and out, and it has dual owner's suites! Double front porches and mature landscaping greet you as you enter the home to discover luxurious features including crown molding, wood flooring, and an open floor plan. To the left of the entry is the formal dining room with lots of natural light. To the right is the family room with a cozy gas fireplace. Pass through the eat-in area to get to the well-appointed kitchen with granite countertops, white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and access to the backyard.The main level owner's suite has a huge en-suite bath with a dual sink vanity, lots of storage, a step-in shower a garden tub, and a huge walk-in closet. On the second level, a second owner's suite has access to the upper porch, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bath with a dual sink vanity, a garden tub, and a step-in shower. Two additional bedrooms, both with en-suite baths and one with access to the porch, and a loft space complete the second level. The screened porch is a wonderful place to enjoy the outdoors and views of the fenced-in backyard. There is also a detached two-car garage as well. This property is located just 1.4 miles from Historic Downtown Summerville, 2.9 miles from Nexton Square, and 16.9 miles from Charleston International Airport. Come see what makes this home so special!
